"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/u4f6KeZuwJXlrBK7dUxPf.png?height=306&width=1640)\\n\\n**January 8th，GMT+1  3：00pm.**\\n\\n**Notetaker: Edwin**\\n\\n————————————————————————————————————————\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/wdGDxJzuijvTHcAqcg2uJ.jpg?height=2448&width=3264)\\n\\n**Roadshow Topic：**What is ShremHouse？\\n\\n**Host：**William、Dylan、Stitch、Arthur\\n\\n**Guest**：（acronym）J-i, F-r, N-i, J-i, E-m, T-hi, E-r, K-i，W-i, T-h\\n\\n**Detail：**\\n\\n1. Introducing ShremHouse\\n2. The development path of Shremhouse\\n\\nWilliam ：Hello, I am William，Thank you for participating in our roadshow.\\n\\nIt's an honor to be brought to the fore by the community to explain what the ShremHouse is? And what will we achieve? I had the idea of creating a decentralized organization for a long time. It was around that time in 2014 when Dr. Gavin Wood of Polkadot first proposed the concept of Web3.0, and I was very attracted. Those who hold the core power in this world cannot do evil in a small cage, because they will be watched by everyone…\\n\\n……\\n\\nShremHouse is a true DAO, and what it wants to do is determined entirely by its members: a charity proposal can accept donations from people all over the world, and members can decide how the donations are used; freelancers can create a network of contractors who Use funds for office space and software subscriptions; a VC proposal could create a venture fund, pool investment capital and vote for VCs, and repayments could be redistributed among Shrem members.\\n\\n……\\n\\n**Initiator**\\n\\n> Initial Co-founder: Stitch Wong, Arthur, Edwin, Colin\\n\\n> Oversea Team: Arthur, William, Dylan, Chris …\\n\\n> Tech-Team: Dylan, Alberto, Jay, Harry, Suna, Edmond …\\n\\n> And the last but not the least: GameGuild Community, Shrem DAO, International Ambassador …\\n\\n**Dylan**\\nTech-Leader, PhD in Edge computing and BlockChain, UiO. Msc in ICT Innovation, TU Berlin and KTH. Over 5 years experiences in IT projects. CTO&Co-founder of Citycharge AS, a powerbank sharing platform launched in Norway and Sweden. 6 Patents in IoT and published several high quality paper.\\n\\n**Jay**\\nIT security expert, former security architect in Microsoft, Huawei, and UAE National Security Research Institute. Over 10 years of experience in security and distributed systems, with 10+ academic papers and two patents.\\n\\n**Stitch**\\nOver 5 years of experience in project management and operation in China. Helped to incubate and operate over 10 crypto projects as well as community construction. Worked in crypto institution of China for 3 years. Successful investor in cryptocurrency market.\\n\\n**Arthur**\\nPhD in Big data analysis of Healthcare; Cryptocurrency believers. Rich experience in crypto community construction. Private investor in cryptocurrency projects. DAOist.\\n\\n**Edwin**\\nOver 3 years of experience in project development and operation, as well as crypto community construction. Helped to incubate and operate over 5 crypto projects. Worked in crypto institution of China for 2 years. DAOist.\\n\\n**Colin**\\nCryptocurrency analyst, successful NFT collector and operator;\\nParticipated in several early GameFi projects; crypto content creator.\\n\\nTwitter: <https://twitter.com/ShremHouse>\\n\\nTelegram: <https://t.me/ShremHouseDAO>\",\"timestamp\":1641894985,\"title\":\"Roadshow record-January 8th，GMT+1  3：00pm\"},\"digest\":\"AnoKkIrHx9m3MuhkAnk2YuN1whirs0J9S_lp54gVuxI\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x804360eFb4c5c1304dE7CE23e2BBE0E154E7fE2b\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Q3we8ra2RgWjyAUt_7gVYxOJq-nFq_TQw3W-4b3XIio\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"-sKj_vTVqW4DTQTCzrmgPGGOJDuBrbd9Nst0X9MHoRM\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"gpTwHodWwxMo5vMZ0sVA8c91BTB4f9hsj43isg_26pwyRggNfr3itke1dlOdglbL0CQJifdh1dvGyHhmUM1otw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x32205708d916b1924e